      "table_notes": [
        "Note 1: Gross Receipts includes all sales less taxes and refunds/discounts/coupons",
        "Note 2: Grand Opening Advertising - $10,000 ($5,000 for transfers/relocations), non-refundable",
        "Note 3: Corporate Ad Fund - 1.0% currently, may increase to 6%. Amounts may be reallocated between funds",
        "Note 4: Cooperative Ad Fund - currently inactive/not required",
        "Note 5: National Media Fund - 4.0%, may increase to 6%. 2024: 96.3% media placement",
        "Note 6: Audit - if 2%+ discrepancy, franchisee pays all inspection costs",
        "Note 7-11: Various operational fees",
        "Note 12: Transfer fee $15,000 for administrative/overhead/legal costs",
        "Note 13: Replacement training $2,500 for Phases 1 and 3 (360 hours)",
        "Note 14-18: Additional assistance, continuing education, maintenance, enforcement, relocation fees",
        "Note 19: Bookkeeping ~$150/week for Coach Rod Smith participants only",
        "Note 20: Indemnification - franchisee not Company's agent",
        "Note 22: Liquidated damages formula detailed"
      ]
